Class JwtAssertionInterceptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.trajano.ms.vertx.jaxrs.JwtAssertionInterceptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.ws.rs.container.ContainerRequestFilter

    @Component
 @Provider
 @Priority(value=2001)
public class JwtAssertionInterceptor
extends Object
implements javax.ws.rs.container.ContainerRequestFilter
    This performs assertion check on the header data. It ignores the /jwks and /swagger URLs which should be publicly accessible.
    Author:
    Archimedes Trajano
